hi folks, and welcome to my author page. i am a: a tech-illiterate redneck, and b: don’t really give a shit as long as this thing functions<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-1')">1</a></sup>, so there’s just a listpages table i stole from <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.wikidot.com/gee0765-s-author-page">gee0765's author page</a>, some commentary i’ll add later, some sick rock and bluegrass songs you should listen to<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-2" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-2')">2</a></sup>, and also my dog, because she’s a dog and that’s pretty cute.
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Thank&nbsp;you</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Thank&nbsp;you</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Just over 2 years ago at the time I'm writing this, I was a <em>terrible</em> writer. However, more importantly, I was a terrible person, and terribly repressed. If I hadn't found this community when I did, and if it hadn't been as kind and corrective as it was, I simply would not be where I am now as a person and a writer. I've been able to understand that I'm pansexual and genderfluid, and been able to realize that the propaganda I've been fed about how happily being those things is sinful and depraved wasn't true. I'm a happier person as a direct result of this community's openness, acceptance, and willingness to give second chances.</p>
<p>So, thank you all, and please consider keeping in mind the impact the culture that's been built here can have, and work to preserve and improve it.</p>
</div>
